# 📊 Retail Analytics & RFM Customer Intelligence Dashboard

An end-to-end retail analytics dashboard built with **Python** and **Streamlit**, analyzing 500,000+ e-commerce transactions to surface business performance metrics and customer-level insights through RFM (Recency, Frequency, Monetary) segmentation.

Built as a data analyst portfolio project using the UCI **Online Retail** dataset — a real transactional dataset from a UK-based online gift retailer.

---

## 🚀 Live Features

### 📈 Page 1 — Business Overview
- Key metrics: **Total Revenue, Total Customers, Average Order Value, Return Rate**
- Monthly **revenue trend** analysis
- **Geographic breakdown** across 30+ countries
- **Top-performing products** and **category-wise revenue** analysis
- Interactive country filter

### 👤 Page 2 — Customer RFM Analysis
- **RFM segmentation** of every customer (Champions, Loyal Customers, At Risk, Lost, New Customers, etc.)
- **Searchable customer lookup** with segment filtering
- Individual **RFM score radar chart**
- **Personalized marketing recommendations** based on customer segment
- Full customer profile: location, purchase history, financial summary
- Top products and category breakdown per customer

